             deposed to that of the prisoner's confession.</p>
               <p>The prisoner had nothing to say, but called his master, Mr. Cole, to his character, whom he had served about five years and a half, and who deposed he had behaved well, but latterly he had got a trick of idling his time away, &amp;c.</p>
